# Chapadevs Design Pattern

IT consultancy focused on small business, with a big-company design. Modern, sharp, professional.

## Color Palette

Use CSS variables from `styles.css`. Do not introduce new greens or colors outside this palette.

| Role | Variable | Hex | Usage |
|------|----------|-----|-------|
| Primary | `--primary-green` | #059669 | Buttons, links, accents, active states |
| Primary Dark | `--primary-green-dark` | #047857 | Hover states, pressed |
| Primary Light | `--primary-green-light` | #10b981 | Highlights, secondary accents |
| Background | `--background` | #ffffff | Cards, surfaces |
| Background Gray | `--background-gray` | #f9fafb | Page background, subtle sections |
| Background Light Green | `--background-light-green` | #ecfdf5 | Hero, soft green tints |
| Text Primary | `--text-primary` | #111827 | Headings, main text (near black) |
| Text Secondary | `--text-secondary` | #374151 | Subtext |
| Text Light | `--text-light` | #6b7280 | Muted text, captions |
| Border | `--border` | #e5e7eb | Borders, dividers |

**Avoid**: Neon greens (#00ff87), blue accents, purple, or colors outside this palette.

## Typography

- **Headings**: `font-family: 'Code Bold', monospace`
- **Buttons / Nav / Emphasis**: `font-family: 'Creato Display Medium', serif`
- **Body**: `font-family: 'Coolvetica', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif`
- **Buttons**: `font-weight: 800`

## Page Title (h1)

Use for main page titles (e.g. Dashboard, Projects). Sharp green accent bar on the left:

```css
.page-title,
.dashboard-header h1 {
  font-family: "Code Bold", monospace;
  font-size: 2rem;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin: 0;
  padding-left: 1rem;
  border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-green);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}
```

