## Header Button Style

Reference pattern for nav and header buttons:

```css
.header-btn {
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 0;
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--primary-green);
  font-family: 'Creato Display Medium', serif;
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  min-width: 90px;
  height: 42px;
  transition: color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
}

.header-btn:hover {
  background: rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1);
  color: var(--primary-green-dark);
}

/* Primary/CTA (e.g. Login) */
.header-btn--primary {
  background: var(--primary-green);
  color: #FFFFFF !important;
}

.header-btn--primary:hover {
  background: var(--primary-green-dark);
  color: #FFFFFF !important;
}
```

## Main Page / Hero Button Style

```css
.btn {
  padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
  border: 2px solid var(--primary-green);
  border-radius: 0;
  font-family: 'Creato Display Medium', serif;
  font-weight: 800;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.btn--primary {
  background: #FFFFFF;
  color: var(--primary-green);
  border-color: var(--primary-green);
}

.btn--primary:hover {
  background: var(--primary-green);
  color: #FFFFFF;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}
```

